details.name: UEFA European Under-17 Championship
details.text: The UEFA European Under-17 Championship or simply UEFA Under-17 Championship, is an annual football competition contested by the European men's under-17 national teams of the member associations of UEFA.

details.name: The Hawthorns
details.text: The Hawthorns is an all-seater football stadium in West Bromwich, West Midlands, England, with a capacity of 26,688.

details.text: The UEFA European Under-21 Championship, the UEFA Under-21 Championship or simply the Euro Under-21, is a biennial football competition contested by the European men's under-21 national teams of the UEFA member associations.
